I'm going to clean up that cafÃ©, Frank.

20:52.142 --> 20:55.062
I'm going to clean it up right now.

20:58.774 --> 20:59.775
Well...

21:00.818 --> 21:03.070
...maybe first thing in the morning.

21:03.403 --> 21:05.906
You don't have to worry about a thing.

21:06.448 --> 21:07.574
Okay?

21:08.700 --> 21:09.743
Okay-

