22:24.026 --> 22:25.152
Please...

22:26.195 --> 22:27.446
...somebody...

22:29.156 --> 22:30.449
...help us.

27:17.903 --> 27:19.363
Frank.

29:25.280 --> 29:27.241
Where's the goddamn toaster?

