Good morning. Island Manor.

30:07.614 --> 30:09.992
Can I help you? Hello?

30:10.576 --> 30:11.660
Hello ?

30:15.414 --> 30:17.541
Faye, what is this?

30:44.234 --> 30:46.695
Come on, Tommy, slow down!

30:47.196 --> 30:48.071
No.

30:49.114 --> 30:51.116
Wait a minute! Those are my pictures!

30:51.200 --> 30:52.826
Wait! Would you stop?

30:52.910 --> 30:54.578
Stop! Just wait!

30:55.871 --> 30:56.872
God.

30:57.247 --> 30:59.374
Today they collect the garbage...

31:17.267 --> 31:18.310
- Hi.
- Hi.

31:18.393 --> 31:21.355
It's all right. It's me, 3B.

31:22.564 --> 31:24.024
Someone was in my room.

31:24.108 --> 31:25.818
Yeah, me too.

31:26.193 --> 31:28.195
I think we got elves.

31:28.278 --> 31:29.905
- Good morning.
- Hi.

31:30.155 --> 31:31.698
- Who are you?
- 3C.

31:32.074 --> 31:34.159
The old Grandey place.

31:34.243 --> 31:37.704
Say, have either of you seen my...

31:38.914 --> 31:41.458
Come on, dear. Don't be shy.

31:41.959 --> 31:43.335
Dear, come on.

31:43.418 --> 31:45.337
Let me get a nice big bolt for you.

31:45.421 --> 31:48.090
You're tired of nails. Here.

31:49.591 --> 31:51.051
You want some paperclips?

31:51.135 --> 31:52.845
Come on. Don't move.

31:52.928 --> 31:55.597
Come on, Faye. Time to go back downstairs.

31:55.764 --> 31:58.600
I'm feeding them. They like this stuff.

31:59.643 --> 32:00.561
Here.

32:03.230 --> 32:05.566
Our son kept birds.

32:05.649 --> 32:08.318
You know, pigeons.

32:09.778 --> 32:12.531
Please, Faye. Don't do this.

32:12.739 --> 32:14.658
Not now, okay?

32:16.827 --> 32:19.163
That's my frying pan.

32:20.414 --> 32:21.415
What?

32:22.207 --> 32:24.001
- Nothing.
-Go ahead. Tell him.

32:24.084 --> 32:27.838
- Nothing. It's not important.
-That's her pan and my coffeepot.

32:30.174 --> 32:32.176
Come on. Come on.

32:33.469 --> 32:35.429
No more pigeons, hon.

32:35.637 --> 32:37.723
It's time to stop.

32:38.974 --> 32:40.726
I said stop that!

32:40.893 --> 32:41.727
Frank.

32:41.810 --> 32:43.145
My God, Faye.

32:43.228 --> 32:45.314
<i>You went into these people's apartments?</i>

32:45.397 --> 32:47.858
Not me, them, the little guys.

32:47.941 --> 32:51.195
Faye, I need you to be with me now.

32:51.278 --> 32:53.322
I need you to be here.

32:53.530 --> 32:55.699
I'm here, Papa. I'm with you.

32:56.116 --> 32:58.035
Now, what else did you take?

32:58.285 --> 33:00.287
I told you, nothing.

33:00.621 --> 33:03.123
-It's the little guys.
-Skip that.

33:03.832 --> 33:05.209
What about this?

33:05.501 --> 33:07.586
Where did you get a new picture?

33:08.087 --> 33:10.297
It's not new, it's fixed.

33:11.006 --> 33:12.591
Fixed like new?

33:12.674 --> 33:15.511
- They did a good job.
-Who did?

33:16.470 --> 33:17.846
I ain't saying.

33:17.930 --> 33:19.264
Goddamn it, Faye!

33:19.348 --> 33:20.766
It's okay. No harm done.

33:20.849 --> 33:22.392
It could be giant rats.

33:22.476 --> 33:24.478
Yeah, from Brooklyn, you know.

33:32.611 --> 33:34.113
That was no rat.

33:34.196 --> 33:35.239
What was it?

33:35.322 --> 33:37.741
Who in his right mind stands in a puddle...

33:37.825 --> 33:40.369
...and sticks a fork in a wall socket?

33:40.786 --> 33:43.497
Come on, get back. All of you.

33:45.582 --> 33:46.792
Come on, now.

33:46.875 --> 33:49.169
There, wait there. Wait there.

33:53.549 --> 33:54.675
Here.

33:55.509 --> 33:56.802
They're shy.

34:54.610 --> 34:55.860
They're the fixers.

34:55.944 --> 34:57.654
They like to fix things.

34:57.821 --> 34:59.531
They have that knack.

35:00.699 --> 35:03.118
Dance me around, Papa.

35:04.203 --> 35:05.829
Oh, come on, you kids.

35:06.663 --> 35:09.625
Put a little Fred Astaire into it.

35:58.173 --> 35:59.842
No, they're not toys.

35:59.925 --> 36:01.844
You can't buy them at Macy's.

36:01.969 --> 36:04.096
The Army told me to call you.

36:05.180 --> 36:06.974
Are you missing anything...

36:07.057 --> 36:10.227
...in the way of experimental aircraft?

36:10.310 --> 36:12.646
Not a word, not even in the Post.

36:12.729 --> 36:15.941
Well, they're robots, right?
They're autogiros or smart bombs.

36:16.024 --> 36:17.568
They're microchip hovercraft.

36:17.651 --> 36:20.779
They're spaceships.
You can tell by looking at them.

36:20.863 --> 36:21.738
Spaceships?

36:21.822 --> 36:24.324
Sure, from a very small planet.

36:25.492 --> 36:26.660
Very small.

36:56.315 --> 36:58.025
Maybe this is all a dream.

36:58.108 --> 37:01.236
If this is a dream, which one of us is having it?

37:02.654 --> 37:03.947
Don't look at me.

37:04.031 --> 37:07.117
I stopped dreaming along time ago.

37:24.802 --> 37:25.844
I'll talk to it.

37:25.928 --> 37:27.805
You better be careful.

37:33.811 --> 37:34.853
Stop!

37:47.950 --> 37:50.577
Welcome to America.

